metadata.name: Zangbeto Masqurade
metadata.description:
Zangbeto Masquerade is one major Masquerade that is significant in the Beninnes culture in Africa. It is known to be the guardian of the night.This masquerade act as traditional security agent that moves across the communities especially in the night watching over people and there properties, tracking down criminals and presenting them to the community to be punished. Zangbeto scares away the enemies, detect thieves and witches, protect law and order. 
The mysterious thing about zangbeto Masquerade is that it Wades.
